{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4b8773e81a","title":"给赫鲁晓夫的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"468dc59f10","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":17,"articleId":"4b8773e81a"},{"id":"9e0ae2e841","index":1,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"4b8773e81a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"d1b36af7d3","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"赫鲁晓夫，当时任苏共中央第一书记、苏联部长会议主席。"},{"id":"40d25ccd96","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈毅，当时任国务院副总理兼外交部部长。"},{"id":"494af12a0d","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"艾森豪威尔，当时任美国总统。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c3e64f75cc","type":"title","text":"给赫鲁晓夫\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a"},{"id":"d1b36af7d3","type":"paragraph","text":"请总理带交陈毅同志办。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a"},{"id":"40d25ccd96","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a"},{"id":"494af12a0d","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十七日亲爱的赫鲁晓夫同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a"},{"id":"927206f659","type":"paragraph","text":"您8月7日给我的信和附来的您同艾森豪威尔所交换的信件副本已经由苏联驻华大使馆转交给我。非常感谢您的这项通知。美国在被道的情况下不得不邀请您去访问，这是苏联和平外交政策义一次重大的胜利。我深信，即将到来的您对美国的访问必将使美国好战分子们处于更加被动的地位。祝您在争取和缓国际紧张局势的斗争中获得新的、更大的成就。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4b8773e81a"},{"id":"3bdbac1d0b","type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义敬礼！","index"